comments.body:
I'd like to take this one. Really clear write-up.
@iancarrasco-b10 quick question before I start — would you prefer the server-side silence trim, or the mini-ICL prefix? I'd lean toward the trim first (detect where speech actually starts and cut the leading silence, carefully so soft sounds don't get clipped). I can test it on an H100/H200 with your 40-sample setup.
Happy to do the other approach if you'd rather.
